Preheat oven to 250 degrees F. Combine KELLOGG'S CRISPIX cereal and walnuts in 13 x 9 x 2-inch baking pan. Pour melted butter over cereal mixture while stirring. Stir together sugar and cinnamon. Sprinkle over cereal mixture, stirring to coat evenly. Bake 45 minutes, stirring every 15 minutes. Gently stir in apples. Spread on paper towel to cool.